Queens Boulevard east from 69th Street, showing a contemplated widening of the Boulevard. View No. 2 shows buildings either partially in or on the street line. From left (partially seen) to right (dormer windows) are buildings owned or occupied in 1873 by J. Gebring, J. Frank, Conrad Stehling, and the Krupp brothers respectively.

March 1925.
View 2: February 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
